item.title: About
item.description: Hello! My name is Tony Miller. I’m a husband, father and software developer living in Australia. I learn something new quite often so I figured I’d share small bits and pieces of what I learnt with whoever can find and see it. English is not my native language so bear with me =). The design of this web site is courtesy to Stephen Siegert Cheers!
